titles.title: To approve the extension of nondiscriminatory treatment with respect to the products of Romania.

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on Ways and Means.

committee.name: House Committee on Ways and Means

action.text: Referred to the Subcommittee on Trade.

bill.summary: 1/6/1993--Introduced. Approves the extension of nondiscriminatory treatment (most-favored-nation treatment) to the products of Romania pursuant to the message transmitted to the Congress by the President on June 22, 1992.
